data.description: Welcome to this nice home on a corner large lot with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, 2 car garage, and much more! Home features a cozy living room with brick fireplace, kitchen with dining area, and access to the large backyard.  Master bedroom offers two closets, full bathroom, & ceiling fan.  Huge backyard features a covered patio, several fruit trees, enough space for entertainment, gardening, and additional parking for larger cars, boats and even RV parking! Property located at a walking distance to Valverde Park which offers playground, tennis courts, & basketball Courts. Close to Shopping and major freeways.
